Package: metacsv
Title: Read and Write CSV Files With Metadata
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Paul",
           family = "McElhany",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "paul.mcelhany@noaa.gov",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9826-755X"))
Description: This package provides functions to read and write csv data files 
    that have metadata embedded at the top of the data file or in a seperate, 
    associated csv file that includes the metadata. A number of standard formats
    for metadata fields are available, but the package is fexible to allow for
    user defined formats. All metadata is in human readable and editable csv
    format.
